*Snow Tech looks onto the incoming Lightning bolts fired from Hurricane. 
Instead of running away from his obvious doom, he froze on the spot 
clenching his hands under his chin and screaming at the top of his lungs.*

"Eeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee!!"

* All the while, Shadow Cat watched with amusment from her hiding place in 
the bushes. He was such a moron sometimes. She rolled her eyes and stood up. 
It was time to save him, again. She Ran over to him and pushed him out of 
the way, the bolts would do her no harm, she could control them, he 
couldn't. She felt them hit her and coarse through her body. It didn't hurt 
her, but the force of the blast knocked her to the ground. She groaned, she 
really should hire a baby sitter for him, and passed out.*

* Snow Tech felt a shove and flew to the ground, hitting his face on a rock. 
He squeeled and sat up, clutching his nose and looking cross-eyed. He 
muttered something about how rude some bots are and turned around to find 
Shadow Cat unconcience. He gasped and ran to her side, lifting his head he 
howled(or, to be more percise, caterwalted).*

" Noooooooooooooooooooooooooo!! Shaddy!"

* He looked at Hurricane. His eyes turning a bright, erie green. He growled 
and advanced menacingly towards the bot. He growled out a single sentance to 
the other bot before he attacked...*

" THAT was MY SISTER!!!!!!"

* Snow Tech spread his wings and lifted off into the sky. He turned on his 
auto ice-rockets and aimed them at hurricane. He smiled, showing all his 
canines and started firing them on turbo.*
